WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.488 --> 00:00:02.608
Two areas of inventory management

2
00:00:02.608 --> 00:00:04.349
that are related to each other

3
00:00:04.349 --> 00:00:07.589
are purchasing and inventory control.

4
00:00:07.589 --> 00:00:11.619
Select each image to learn more about these areas.

5
00:00:11.619 --> 00:00:13.909
On the purchasing side, one must order

6
00:00:13.909 --> 00:00:17.309
the correct quantities at the time for the right prices

7
00:00:17.309 --> 00:00:19.589
from the appropriate vendors.

8
00:00:19.589 --> 00:00:23.440
Inventory is the logical result of the action of purchasing.

9
00:00:23.440 --> 00:00:25.968
Therefore, to manage your inventory,

10
00:00:25.968 --> 00:00:28.918
you need to manage your purchasing process.

11
00:00:28.918 --> 00:00:31.579
Proper levels should be set for items in the inventory

12
00:00:31.579 --> 00:00:34.811
to determine when to reorder the needed item.

